heat transfer in turbulent shear flow ..Arannie,w.d..Bj. ae. scs. 23, 1956..Wheat transfer in turbulent shear flow .  the problems of heat transfer in turbulent shear flow along asmooth wall are discussed from the point of view of von karman'swell-known 1939 paper on the analogy between fluid friction andheat transfer .  methods for extending the analysis to higherprandtl numbers are suggested .